Package de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message.tnccs.batch

TNCCS batch interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TnccsBatch
    Generic TNCCS message batch base consisting of a batch header and a set of TNCCS messages.
    TnccsBatchHeader
    Generic TNCCS message batch header base consisting of general parameters, that describe a batch.
    TnccsBatchHeaderBuilder
    Generic builder base to build a TNCCS message batch header.
